Dialogue: 1,0:00:18.67,0:00:25.38,OP - CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,200)\blur2\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&\t(2331,2331,\c&H000000&\3c&HFFFFFF&)}命运正召唤着我们登上这盛大舞台
Dialogue: 1,0:00:26.67,0:00:31.93,OP - CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}胸膛里聚光灯闪耀  脑海中思绪沸腾
Dialogue: 1,0:00:33.39,0:00:39.65,OP - CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&\t(5010,5010,\3c&HFFFFFF&\c&H000000&)}追梦路上  我们前赴后继洒下热泪
Dialogue: 1,0:00:40.65,0:00:44.73,OP - CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}即使唱到心碎  仍愿相信
Dialogue: 1,0:00:45.03,0:00:47.65,OP - CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,0)\blur2}曙光就等在前方
Dialogue: 1,0:00:47.65,0:00:51.11,OP - CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,200)\blur2}你和我  共携手
Dialogue: 1,0:00:51.11,0:00:54.41,OP - CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}奔赴到路尽头
Dialogue: 1,0:00:54.74,0:00:58.41,OP - CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,0)\blur2}夜空下我们也可向星辰许愿
Dialogue: 1,0:00:58.41,0:01:02.17,OP - CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,200)\blur2}向着光来的方向
Dialogue: 1,0:01:03.34,0:01:07.01,OP - CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}勇敢伸出手吧  抓住那伟大的愿望
Dialogue: 1,0:01:07.01,0:01:10.68,OP - CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}不用管它是否是别人眼中的白日梦
Dialogue: 1,0:01:10.68,0:01:14.85,OP - CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}就算「最闪耀的星星将最早迎来熄灭」
Dialogue: 1,0:01:14.85,0:01:18.18,OP - CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,0)\blur2}我们也会打破这命运
Dialogue: 1,0:01:18.18,0:01:21.44,OP - CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}面对无人可知的明天
Dialogue: 1,0:01:21.44,0:01:25.32,OP - CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,200)\blur2}只需听从内心的声音
Dialogue: 1,0:01:25.32,0:01:28.94,OP - CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,0)\blur2}去奔跑  去超越
Dialogue: 1,0:01:28.94,0:01:30.78,OP - CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,200)\blur2}将梦与未来
Dialogue: 1,0:01:30.78,0:01:35.20,OP - CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}交织在一起
Dialogue: 1,0:01:36.45,0:01:38.79,OP - CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}用我最珍贵的誓言
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.67,0:00:25.38,OP - JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,200)\blur2\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&\t(2331,2331,\c&H000000&\3c&HFFFFFF&)}hey, 運命が呼んでいる{\fscx50} {\fscx100}for the big stage
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.67,0:00:31.93,OP - JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}the spotlight filling my heart{\fscx50} {\fscx100}また熱くなる想い
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.39,0:00:39.65,OP - JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&\t(5010,5010,\3c&HFFFFFF&\c&H000000&)}Ah, 夢追って淚した{\fscx50} {\fscx100}ones before me
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.65,0:00:44.73,OP - JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}I sing through the heartbreak{\fscx50} {\fscx100}信じたい
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.03,0:00:47.65,OP - JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,0)\blur2}光が待っている
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.65,0:00:51.11,OP - JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,200)\blur2}I've got you You've got me
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.11,0:00:54.41,OP - JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}最後まで進んで
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.74,0:00:58.41,OP - JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,0)\blur2}Oh in the night we can wish on a star
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.41,0:01:02.17,OP - JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,200)\blur2}光の先へ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.34,0:01:07.01,OP - JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}手を伸ばし続けた{\fscx50} {\fscx100}big dream
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.01,0:01:10.68,OP - JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}誰かの目には{\fscx50} {\fscx100}it's a daydream
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.68,0:01:14.85,OP - JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}“All the stars that shine brightest, Burn out the fastest”
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.85,0:01:18.18,OP - JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,0)\blur2}ぼくら越えていける
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.18,0:01:21.44,OP - JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}誰も知らない{\fscx50} {\fscx100}tomorrow
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.44,0:01:25.32,OP - JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,200)\blur2}心の声だけ{\fscx50} {\fscx100}follow
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.32,0:01:28.94,OP - JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,0)\blur2}駆け抜けたい
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.94,0:01:30.78,OP - JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,200)\blur2}夢と未来
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.78,0:01:35.20,OP - JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}重なるように
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.45,0:01:38.79,OP - JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}with my pledge
Dialogue: 3,0:22:10.69,0:22:18.36,ED - CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}曾经对着镜子拭去眼泪  追逐梦想
Dialogue: 3,0:22:18.48,0:22:21.95,ED - CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}在那个地方
Dialogue: 3,0:22:23.49,0:22:30.66,ED - CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}连好好给自己一个拥抱都做不到的懊悔
Dialogue: 3,0:22:30.66,0:22:36.09,ED - CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}和自尊一同  在房间中回荡
Dialogue: 3,0:22:36.25,0:22:42.76,ED - CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}珍贵的时间渐渐被夺走
Dialogue: 3,0:22:42.76,0:22:49.89,ED - CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}现今我正走在那条
Dialogue: 3,0:22:49.89,0:22:54.65,ED - CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}不曾放弃追寻的理想之路上
Dialogue: 3,0:22:54.65,0:22:57.65,ED - CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}要以比那时更为充实的自己
Dialogue: 3,0:22:57.65,0:23:03.11,ED - CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}去同回忆相会
Dialogue: 3,0:23:04.16,0:23:10.50,ED - CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}即使身处告别之中
Dialogue: 3,0:23:10.50,0:23:17.04,ED - CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}我们也在不断堆砌各自的理想
Dialogue: 3,0:23:17.04,0:23:21.17,ED - CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}虽然与梦中盼望的那个日子
Dialogue: 3,0:23:21.17,0:23:28.01,ED - CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}仍然相距甚远
Dialogue: 3,0:23:28.01,0:23:31.27,ED - CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}但我还是想将其留到未来
Dialogue: 3,0:23:31.27,0:23:34.48,ED - CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}为了将来的我
Dialogue: 3,0:23:34.48,0:23:38.02,ED - CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,500)}能够由衷展露笑颜
Dialogue: 1,0:22:10.69,0:22:18.36,ED - JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}鏡に向かい涙を拭き夢を追ってた
Dialogue: 1,0:22:18.48,0:22:21.95,ED - JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}あの場所には
Dialogue: 1,0:22:23.49,0:22:30.66,ED - JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}自分を抱きしめてあげられない悔しさ
Dialogue: 1,0:22:30.66,0:22:36.09,ED - JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}プライドが部屋を交差してた
Dialogue: 1,0:22:36.25,0:22:42.76,ED - JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}大事な時間が奪われていく
Dialogue: 1,0:22:42.76,0:22:49.89,ED - JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}諦めず探した理想の道を今
Dialogue: 1,0:22:49.89,0:22:54.65,ED - JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}歩いてあの頃以上に
Dialogue: 1,0:22:54.65,0:22:57.65,ED - JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}満たされた私で
Dialogue: 1,0:22:57.65,0:23:03.11,ED - JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}思い出に会いにいくよ
Dialogue: 1,0:23:04.16,0:23:10.50,ED - JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}さようならの中でも
Dialogue: 1,0:23:10.50,0:23:17.04,ED - JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}それぞれ理想積み上げてたんだ
Dialogue: 1,0:23:17.04,0:23:21.17,ED - JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}夢焦がれたあの日には
Dialogue: 1,0:23:21.17,0:23:28.01,ED - JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}程遠いみたいだけどまだ
Dialogue: 1,0:23:28.01,0:23:31.27,ED - JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}未来にとっておくよ
Dialogue: 1,0:23:31.27,0:23:34.48,ED - JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}これからの私を
Dialogue: 1,0:23:34.48,0:23:38.02,ED - JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,500)}楽しめるように
